<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>后台欢迎页</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      /* 设置背景图片，覆盖整个页面 */
      background-image: url('/images/background.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: "微软雅黑", sans-serif;
    }

    /* 文字容器，添加半透明背景让文字更清晰 */
    .welcome-text {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }

    .welcome-text h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .welcome-text p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #f0f0f0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="welcome-text">
    <h1>后台管理系统</h1>
    <p>欢迎使用管理系统</p>
    <p>请从左侧菜单选择功能</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
